# Private repository

This workspace is the **internal Hyperspeed codebase** (private). There is **no** separate “public OSS” export path, cherry-pick workflow, or requirement to coordinate with a public `main`.

## Contributors and agents

- Use normal **branch and PR** (or equivalent) discipline for risky changes.
- Do **not** assume end users clone from a public URL or follow generic self-host instructions aimed at outside teams—docs in this repo describe **our** deployment and operations unless explicitly marked otherwise.

## Local git hooks

Optional: run `scripts/setup-git-hooks.ps1` or `scripts/setup-git-hooks.sh` to use `.githooks/` (currently a no-op **pre-push**; extend there if the team adds checks).
